<text name="tip_fr_fish_food">Tip: Check the storage menu to use the fish.</text>
<text name="tip_fr_revenant">Tip: Revenant weapons are mysterious pieces of technology forged in the depths of Tartarus. They are very strong, but often highly specialized.</text>
<text name="tip_fr_wither_crew">Tip: Aenwithe's crew drones do not have the capability to withstand switching modes, and are too complex for Technopaths to replicate. They can, however, be very powerful.</text>
<text name="tip_fr_elite_federation_loot_1">UNITY LOOT
Stuns crew hit for 10 seconds
+30 crew damage 
+1 system damage
-3 seconds cooldown </text>
<text name="tip_fr_elite_federation_loot_2">UNITY LOOT
Stuns crew hit for 10 seconds
+30 crew damage 
+1 system damage
+20% fire and breach chance
-3 seconds cooldown</text>
<text name="tip_fr_elite_federation_loot_3">UNITY LOOT
Stuns crew hit for 2 seconds
+15 crew damage 
+20% fire and +10% breach chance
-3 seconds pre-chain cooldown (final cooldown is the same)</text>
<text name="tip_fr_elite_coalition_loot_1">RUES LOOT
+20% fire and breach chance 
+20% accuracy
-4 seconds cooldown </text>
<text name="tip_fr_elite_coalition_loot_2">RUES LOOT 
+1 projectile fired
+30% breach chance
-2 seconds cooldown </text>
<text name="tip_fr_elite_rebel_loot_1">MFK LOOT
+10% accuracy
+10% fire chance and +20% breach chance
-1.5 second cooldown</text>
<text name="tip_fr_elite_rebel_loot_2">MFK LOOT
+2 shield pierce
+60% fire chance
-1 second cooldown</text>
<text name="tip_fr_elite_auto_loot_1">INNOVATION LOOT
+1 projectile fired
+10 projectile speed
-2 seconds cooldown</text>
<text name="tip_fr_elite_rock_loot_1">INQUISITION LOOT
-15px radius, +10% fire and breach chance
-2 seconds cooldown</text>
<text name="tip_fr_elite_zoltan_loot_1">PEACE-KEEPER LOOT
+1 hull damage
