<text name="addon_hover_fr">FORGOTTEN RACES
    Currently Enabled.
    Click to see more info.</text>
	
<text name="info_addon_fr">FORGOTTEN RACES
    Developed by Gabriel Cooper 
	Ex-Developer: HereticChurch
    Currently Enabled.

	This addon mod brings back the canonically extinct subclass of the Ancients/Obelisks called the "Commonwealth" and also adds content for the almost-extinct Salt race, as well as a new cruiser line for the Osmians.

	Forgotten Races also adds 164 new ships, 121 weapons and drones, 61 new crew members, a revived questline with dozens of unlocks that did not make into the base Multiverse mod, and 3 new Renegade bosses, all with exclusive weapons and gimmicks.

	There are brand new sectors with unique music and questlines:

	A sector featuring the Commonwealth with its own final boss and ending!

	A unique sector, the Warzone. Enter a three way war between the Federation, Rebels and Coalition in hopes of unlocking the Coalition and Federation flagships.
</text>

